query:
SELECT tl.id, tl.lojaId, l.nome as lojaNome, tl.token, tl.ativo, tl.createdAt 
FROM tokens_loja tl 
JOIN lojas l ON tl.lojaId = l.id 
WHERE l.nome LIKE '%Paredes%' 
ORDER BY tl.createdAt DESC 
LIMIT 5;
